      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need some help with a formal email. I'm an HR manager at a logistics company and I have to write a disciplinary email to an employee. They've been about 15 minutes late to their shifts every day for the last two weeks. Can you draft something professional and firm but not like, super aggressive? We want to keep it strictly business.",
